      <section eId="sec_17_0827">
        <num>17-0827</num>
        <heading>Conflicts of interest</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_17_0827__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>"significant portion of his income"\nshall mean ten percent of gross personal income for a calendar year,\nexcept that it shall mean fifty percent of gross personal income for a\ncalendar year if the recipient is over sixty years of age and is\nreceiving such portion pursuant to retirement, pension, or similar\narrangement;</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_17_0827__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>"income" includes retirement benefits, consultant fees,\nand stock dividends; and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_17_0827__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>income is not received "directly or\nindirectly from permit holders or applicants for a permit" where it is\nderived from mutual-fund payments, or from other diversified investments\nover which the recipient does not know the identity of the primary\nsources of income.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
